{"tid":601753,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"三星S9系列隨機出現觸控死區 換新的也一樣","createTime":"2018-03-22T12:49:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-26T06:41:52.000Z","uid":10717,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f78c0145b060234a6c327e43bcffae5f33f57598","tid":601753,"uid":10717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T12:49:03.000Z","msg":"韓國行動裝置大廠三星電子（Samsung Electronics Co.）日前於2018世界通訊大會 (<br />\nMWC2018 ) 上，推出最新旗艦手機  Galaxy S9、S9 ，近日傳出在使用過程中，觸控螢幕<br />\n會隨機出現死區 ( Dead Zone 意即無法點擊的區域 ) ，其出現原因尚不清楚，而之中似<br />\n乎沒有一定的規則。<br />\n<br />\n根據外媒報導，此次死區的災情大部分出現於 S9 ，而 S9 則是部分用戶，這些使用者遭<br />\n遇到的狀況，有的死區出現在螢幕頂端，有些接近底部，若是剛好出現於虛擬按鍵的位置<br />\n上，將會帶來非常多的不便。其實這樣的問題不罕見，但對於三星的手機而言，卻是鮮少<br />\n出現的狀況。對此，除了目前無法釐清發生原因以外，三星也還未有任何表示。<br />\n<br />\n而截至目前為止，三星持續的要求出問題的使用者，將其手機寄回，並藉由保固的服務更<br />\n換全新的手機，但即便如此，許多把手機重新更換過的用戶，在拿到新機後依然遇到同樣<br />\n的問題。<br />\n<br />\nS9又出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89994de4d91a416c4b2a9899f6ef3a83c88c661e","tid":601753,"uid":158977,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T13:08:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://appuals.com/how-to-fix-iphone-x-touch-screen-not-responsive-issue/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappuals.com%2Fhow-to-fix-iphone-x-touch-screen-not-responsive-issue%2F&d=fdLFOeRAS9c9pZiW6anb1iwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=38d83fb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://appuals.com/how-to-fix-iphone-x-touch-screen-not-responsive-issue/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c3fe32facb92adef0784568972af54ebd23e33a","tid":601753,"uid":81397,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"89994de4d91a416c4b2a9899f6ef3a83c88c661e","tid":601753,"uid":158977,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T13:08:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://appuals.com/how-to-fix-iphone-x-touch-screen-not-responsive-issue/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappua